CLOUD SECURITY - INFORMATION SECURITY OBJECTIVES
- Applications, Functions, Services
Examine security vulnerabilities and takesteps to ensure protection
Emphasis on PaaS where the developr is responsible for the security of any application that will be hoseted on a SaaS platform
Emphasis on SaaS platform and its inherent security requirements, the responisibility of which fall almost exclusivy on the SaaS provider

The Cloud Security Alliance (CSA)
- Security guidance for critical areas of focus in cloud computing
